    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment is Accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted based on regulatory precedent for single-condition ASTM F1717 testing and the Medium model risk classification. Several factors (Numerical solver error, Use error, Equivalency of input parameters, Relevance of QoIs, Relevance of validation activities) were assessed at required levels without formal acceptance criteria documentation; the assessment team judged these factors adequately addressed by standard practice for this model risk level.",
